name: 3-oxoacyl-[acyl-carrier-protein] reductase
classes: Acting on the CH-OH group of donors;

reaction: a (3R)-3-hydroxyacyl-[acyl-carrier protein] + NADP+ = a 3-oxoacyl-[acyl-carrier protein] + NADPH + H+ [RN:R02767]
comment: Exhibits a marked preference for acyl-carrier-protein derivatives over CoA derivatives as substrates.
